for tucking me in.

22:16.936 --> 22:21.408
I was hoping Walter would,
but I guess he's too busy.

22:21.474 --> 22:23.042
I'm sure you'll see him
in the morning, Jim.

22:23.142 --> 22:24.977
He cares about you
very much.

22:25.077 --> 22:27.747
That's right, Jim.
And if you have
night terrors,

22:27.847 --> 22:30.817
just scream
and we will come running.

22:30.917 --> 22:32.585
What?

22:34.220 --> 22:38.090
Now, be a good lad
and get some rest.

22:38.190 --> 22:40.893
Oh, I'm not
quite ready to close
my eyes now, Harry.

22:40.993 --> 22:42.995
Time to sleep, Jim.

22:43.095 --> 22:45.965
Yeah, but, Harry,
I just--

22:46.065 --> 22:48.468
I wouldn't fight him, Jim.
He's very strict
about bedtime.

22:48.568 --> 22:50.269
It's true.

22:50.437 --> 22:52.539
Oh!
Okay, okay.

22:52.639 --> 22:55.542
Now, there's a good lad.

23:00.447 --> 23:02.482
Herschel...!

23:47.527 --> 23:50.396
It's okay.
You're drunk.
I know I am.

23:50.497 --> 23:53.132
We're fantastic
together.

23:55.602 --> 23:58.638
You know that lyric
"He's your fella
and you love him"?

24:00.139 --> 24:03.042
