24:06.613 --> 24:10.349
He's probably hearing you
singing in his dreams.

24:10.517 --> 24:12.719
Now, come on,
let's try again.

24:45.117 --> 24:47.186
I want to take
this on.

24:47.286 --> 24:49.922
I want to find those men
who murdered your friend

24:50.022 --> 24:52.391
and who assaulted you.

24:52.559 --> 24:54.927
Walter, please,
let it go.

24:55.027 --> 24:56.929
